Package: admixspatial
Title: Spatial Visualization of ADMIXTURE Results
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sebastian", "Guzman Rodriguez", email = "sebastian.guzman@ufrgs.br", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive R package for visualizing ADMIXTURE results with spatial context. 
    Supports both library usage and command-line interface. Features include cross-validation 
    error plots, admixture bar plots, and spatial maps with automatic geographic data integration.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
